```

Open `.gitignore` in VS Code and paste this — it prevents sensitive files from being uploaded:
```
# Python
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# Django
*.log
local_settings.py
db.sqlite3
media/
staticfiles/

# Environment variables — NEVER upload these
.env
backend/.env

# React / Node
node_modules/
frontend/node_modules/
dist/
frontend/dist/
.DS_Store

# VS Code
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini